description: Launched on 15/01/2019 by Currency.com team based in Gibraltar and Belarus, represents a tokenised version of traditional financial market - 21Vianet Group, Inc. shares on Ethereum blockchain, price of underlined assets is tailored to 21Vianet Group, Inc. market price. Tokenisation of the asset provides possibility to invest to popular financial markets worldwide using crypto.
name: 21Vianet Group, Inc.
